M|paid-ads|**Testing phase (first 2-4 weeks):**
M|paid-ads|- 70% to proven/safe cg
M|paid-ads|- 30% to testing new audiences/creative
M|paid-ads|**Scaling phase:**
M|paid-ads|- Consolidate budget into winning combinations
M|paid-ads|- Increase budgets 20-30% at a time
M|paid-ads|- Wait 3-5 days between increases for algorithm learning
M|paid-ads|**Problem-Agitate-Solve (PAS):**
M|paid-ads|> [Problem] → [Agitate the pain] → [Introduce solution] → [CTA]
M|paid-ads|**Before-After-Bridge (BAB):**
M|paid-ads|> [Current painful state] → [Desired future state] → [Your product as bridge]
M|paid-ads|**soc Proof Lead:**
M|paid-ads|> [Impressive stat or testimonial] → [What you do] → [CTA]
