M|paid-ads|| Platform | Key Targeting | Best Signals |
M|paid-ads||----------|---------------|--------------|
M|paid-ads|| Google | Keywords, search intent | What they're searching |
M|paid-ads|| Meta | Interests, behaviors, lookalikes | Engagement patterns |
