M|paid-ads|- **Lookalikes**: Base on best customers (by LTV), not all customers
M|paid-ads|- **Retargeting**: Segment by funnel stage (visitors vs. cart abandoners)
M|paid-ads|- **Exclusions**: Exclude existing customers and recent converters — showing ads to people who already bought wastes spend
M|paid-ads|**For detailed targeting strategies by platform**: See [references/audience-targeting.md](references/audience-targeting.md)
M|paid-ads|- Clear product screenshots showing UI
M|paid-ads|- Before/after comparisons
M|paid-ads|- Stats and numbers as focal point
M|paid-ads|- Human faces (real, not stock)
M|paid-ads|- Bold, readable text overlay (keep under 20%)
M|paid-ads|1. Hook (0-3 sec): Pattern interrupt, question, or bold statement
M|paid-ads|2. Problem (3-8 sec): Relatable pain point
M|paid-ads|3. Solution (8-20 sec): Show product/benefit
M|paid-ads|4. CTA (20-30 sec): Clear next step
M|paid-ads|**prd tips:**
M|paid-ads|- Captions always (85% watch without sound)
M|paid-ads|- Vertical for Stories/Reels, square for feed
M|paid-ads|- Native feel outperforms polished
M|paid-ads|- First 3 seconds determine if they watch
M|paid-ads|1. Concept/angle (biggest impact)
M|paid-ads|2. Hook/headline
M|paid-ads|3. Visual style
M|paid-ads|4. Body copy
M|paid-ads|5. CTA
