M|paid-ads|| Consideration | CTR, CPC, Time on site |
M|paid-ads|| Conversion | CPA, ROAS, Conversion rate |
M|paid-ads|**If CPA is too high:**
M|paid-ads|1. Check landing page (is the problem post-click?)
M|paid-ads|2. Tighten audience targeting
M|paid-ads|3. Test new creative angles
M|paid-ads|4. Improve ad relevance/quality score
M|paid-ads|5. Adjust bid str
M|paid-ads|**If CTR is low:**
M|paid-ads|- Creative isn't resonating → test new hooks/angles
M|paid-ads|- Audience mismatch → refine targeting
M|paid-ads|- Ad fatigue → refresh creative
M|paid-ads|**If CPM is high:**
M|paid-ads|- Audience too narrow → expand targeting
M|paid-ads|- High competition → try different placements
M|paid-ads|- Low relevance score → improve creative fit
M|paid-ads|1. Start with manual or cost caps
M|paid-ads|2. Gather conversion data (50+ conversions)
M|paid-ads|3. Switch to automated with targets based on historical data
M|paid-ads|4. Monitor and adjust targets based on results
M|paid-ads|| Funnel Stage | Audience | Message | Goal |
M|paid-ads||--------------|----------|---------|------|
M|paid-ads|| Top | Blog readers, video viewers | Educational, soc proof | Move to consideration |
M|paid-ads|| Middle | Pricing/feature page visitors | Case studies, demos | Move to dec |
M|paid-ads|| Bottom | Cart abandoners, trial users | Urgency, objection handling | Convert |
M|paid-ads|| Stage | Window | Frequency Cap |
M|paid-ads||-------|--------|---------------|
M|paid-ads|| Hot (cart/trial) | 1-7 days | Higher OK |
M|paid-ads|| Warm (key pages) | 7-30 days | 3-5x/week |
M|paid-ads|| Cold (any visit) | 30-90 days | 1-2x/week |
M|paid-ads|- Existing customers (unless upsell)
M|paid-ads|- Recent converters (7-14 day window)
M|paid-ads|- Bounced visitors (<10 sec)
M|paid-ads|- Irrelevant pages (careers, support)
